‼️Tattoo collab announcement‼️

Our friend @robwalshtattoos will be visiting Charlotte so you know what that means 🎉 
November 30th-December 2nd we are looking to collaborate on a tattoo!

Rob and I would love to tattoo one of the Hashira or any demon slayer character as a Pokémon trainer with corresponding Pokémon!

To inquire, send either of us an email. Be sure to include your name, pronouns, which hashira you want to get, which date is preferable (11/30-12/2), and a photo of the spot you want it! Legs or arms only.

We are so excited for this and can’t wait to see your ideas! ☺️

Mannnn what a year!!! The year was a rollercoaster to say the least. But this year offered more growth than I’ve ever had. Lost connections, and made new ones. Made wonderful memories and some not so great. Met amazing people and some shitty hahaha, but everything comes with balance. Without the bad it’s hard to appreciate the good. So I appreciate every single thing that has happened to me this year.

Thank you @mikendazzoart for taking a chance and bringing me aboard the Sadfam crew, taking the time to teach me, and always putting the crew first. (Though you need to take more time for yourself lol) I appreciate ya more than ya know!!

And to my clients, thank you for making this life possible. You guys are the real mvps day in and day out. From the ideas you bring me to the good times and laughs shared, I appreciate every one of you for the trust you put in me and letting me bring your ideas to life. Without y’all I’d of never gotten this far, so thank you 🖤🖤

Cheers to the new year everyone!! 🥂
